      • getOlssonThresholdLegibility

        public GridTessellation<Boolean> getOlssonThresholdLegibility(double cellWidth)
        Compute the threshold method for legibility measurement from (Olsson et al 2011).
        Parameters:
        cellWidth -
        Returns:
        a grid with a true value when cells are legible and a false value when cells aren't legible
